==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Elsewhere
<hw>Else"where`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In
any other place; <as>as, these trees are not to be found
<ex>elsewhere</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In some other place; in other places, indefinitely;
<as>as, it is reported in town and <ex>elsewhere</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Elsewhither</ent>⟦br⟧
